      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:18:5",
      "text": [
        " مَنْ لَبِسَ نَعْلًا صَفْرَاءَ كَانَ فِي سُرُورٍ حَتَّى يُبْلِيَهَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companons, from Ahmad Bin Abu Abdullah, from Muhammad Bin Ali, from Abu Al Bakhtary, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The one who wears yellow sandals would be in delight until he renews them’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn abu ‘Abd Allah from Muhammad ibn Ali from abu al-Bakhtariy who has said the following: “If one wears yellow shoes he continues with happiness until that shoe becomes old.’” "
        ]
      }
    },
